  <brief_title>Evaluation of 3APS in Patients With Mild to Moderate Alzheimer’s Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Study of the Efficacy and Safety of 3APS in Patients With Mild to Moderate Alzheimer’s Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Bellus Health Inc</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Bellus Health Inc</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this Phase III study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of 3APS compared
      to placebo (inactive substance pill) in patients with mild to moderate Alzheimer’s disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
