  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The two primary efficacy parameters are the change from baseline to month 18 in the Alzheimer's Disease Assessment Scale, cognitive subpart (ADAS-cog) and the clinical Deterioration Scale Sum of Boxes (CDR-SB) scores.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The brain volume change from baseline as measured by Magnetic Resonance Imaging will also be assessed.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
